# Student Web — UI/UX Design System

> Tài liệu thiết kế hệ thống UI/UX cho **student-web**. Mục tiêu: đảm bảo sự nhất quán về giao diện, tương tác và trải nghiệm người dùng trên toàn bộ ứng dụng học sinh.

---

## 1. Tổng Quan & Nguyên Tắc Thiết Kế

### 1.1 Identity & Positioning
- **Đối tượng**: Học sinh (từ cấp THCS đến THPT / đại học)
- **Tone of Voice**: Năng động, khuyến khích, dễ tiếp cận nhưng vẫn chuyên nghiệp
- **Cách tính**: Soft UI — bo góc lớn (rounded-2xl), shadow mềm, gradient nhẹ, card-based
- **Độ phức tạp**: Thấp đến trung bình — giao diện gọn gàng, tập trung vào hành động chính

### 1.2 Nguyên Tắc Cốt Lõi

1. **Student-Friendly** — Ngôn ngữ đơn giản, icon rõ ràng, hướng dẫn trực quan
2. **Goal-Oriented** — Hiển thị rõ "việc cần làm" (deadline, bài chưa nộp, điểm thấp)
3. **Encouraging** — Sử dụng positive reinforcement (celebration on good grades, progress indicators)
4. **Distraction-Free** — Giảm thiểu clutter, tập trung vào nội dung học tập
5. **Responsive First** — Mobile-first, vì nhiều học sinh dùng điện thoại
6. **Accessible** — WCAG AA compliant, focus states rõ ràng, touch targets ≥ 44px

### 1.3 Color Contrast Compliance
- Văn bản trên nền sáng: contrast ratio ≥ 4.5:1 (WCAG AA)
- Văn bản lớn (≥18px bold / ≥24px regular): ≥ 3:1 (WCAG AA)
- Tất cả màu status cần có icon hoặc text label bổ sung

---

## 2. Design Tokens

### 2.1 Color Palette

#### Primary Colors (Sage Green — Brand)
| Token | Hex | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| `primary` | `#7BA389` | Nút chính, trạng thái active, link, progress |
| `primary-dark` | `#5C8A6E` | Hover state, gradient endpoint |
| `primary-light` | `#9DC4AB` | Background tints, selected items, progress fills |
| `primary-darkest` | `#4A6F5E` | Pressed state, gradient start |

#### Secondary Colors (Blue-Gray)
| Token | Hex | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| `secondary` | `#7B9BA3` | Muted accent, secondary buttons, borders |
| `secondary-light` | `#9DBDC4` | Section headers, info tints, tags |
| `secondary-dark` | `#5C7B83` | Hover for secondary |

#### Accent Colors
| Token | Hex | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| `accent` | `#B3A38B` | Warm tan, upcoming section accent |
| `accent-light` | `#C4B59D` | Warm tints, highlight boxes |
| `mint` | `#A3B38B` | Stats card accent, alternative green |
| `mint-light` | `#B5C49D` | Mint backgrounds, progress variant |

#### Background Colors
| Token | Hex | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| `background` | `#F7FAF9` | Page background (slight green tint) |
| `surface` | `#F9FAFB` | Card background, panels |
| `surface-hover` | `#F3F4F6` | Interactive surface state |
| `white` | `#FFFFFF` | Modal, overlay surface |
| `border` | `#E5E7EB` | Card border, input border |
| `border-light` | `#F3F4F6` | Subtle dividers |

#### Text Colors
| Token | Hex | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| `text-primary` | `#1F2937` | Heading, body chính |
| `text-secondary` | `#6B7280` | Label, description, supporting text |
| `text-muted` | `#9CA3AF` | Placeholder, timestamp, disabled |

#### Status Colors
| Token | BG | Text | Usage |
|---|---|---|---|
| `success` | `#D4E8D7` | `#3D7A4F` | Hoàn thành, đạt điểm cao |
| `warning` | `#FFE8D6` | `#B86E00` | Pending, chưa nộp, sắp hết hạn |
| `error` | `#FDE8E8` | `#C53030` | Lỗi, không đạt, quá hạn |
| `info` | `#DCE4F2` | `#4A6FA5` | Thông tin, đang xử lý |
| `live` | `#DCFCE7` | `#16A34A` | Exam đang diễn ra |

### 2.2 Typography

#### Font Stack
```css
font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', sans-serif;
```

#### Type Scale
| Class | Size | Weight | Line Height | Usage |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| `text-xs` | 12px | 400–600 | 1.5 | Badge, caption, timestamp |
| `text-sm` | 14px | 400–600 | 1.5 | Body nhỏ, label, description |
| `text-base` | 16px | 400 | 1.5 | Body text chính |
| `text-lg` | 18px | 500 | 1.4 | Sub-heading, card title |
| `text-xl` | 20px | 600 | 1.3 | Page section title |
| `text-2xl` | 24px | 700 | 1.2 | Page title |
| `text-3xl` | 30px | 700 | 1.1 | Dashboard hero |

#### Letter Spacing
- Headings: `tracking-tight` (-0.025em)
- Badges: `tracking-wide` (0.025em) for uppercase labels

### 2.3 Spacing System

Sử dụng **4px base unit** (Tailwind scale):

| Token | Value | Common Use |
|---|---|---|
| `space-1` | 4px | Icon padding, micro gaps |
| `space-2` | 8px | Internal component spacing |
| `space-3` | 12px | Badge padding, input padding-y |
| `space-4` | 16px | Card padding, gap between cards |
| `space-5` | 20px | Section padding |
| `space-6` | 24px | Page section gap |
| `space-8` | 32px | Major section divider |
| `space-10` | 40px | Page header spacing |
| `space-12` | 48px | Hero section gap |

### 2.4 Border Radius

| Token | Value | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| `rounded-lg` | 8px | Input, small button |
| `rounded-xl` | 12px | Button, dropdown |
| `rounded-2xl` | 16px | Main card, modal content |
| `rounded-3xl` | 24px | Large card, hero section |
| `rounded-full` | 9999px | Pill, avatar, badge, nav item |
| `rounded-[20px]` | 20px | Status badge (`.badge`) |
| `rounded-[30px]` | 30px | Quick action card (`.qa-card`) |

### 2.5 Shadows

| Token | Value | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| `shadow-sm` | Tailwind default | Subtle lift |
| `shadow-md` | Tailwind default | Card default |
| `shadow-lg` | Tailwind default | Card hover, dropdown |
| `shadow-xl` | Tailwind default | Modal |
| `shadow-soft` | `0 4px 16px -6px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)` | `.card` class |
| `shadow-card` | `0 4px 16px -6px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)` | Card class alias |
| `shadow-button` | `0 2px 8px rgba(46,125,107,0.25)` | Primary button |

### 2.6 Motion & Animation

#### Timing Functions
```css
--transition-elegant: 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
--transition-fast:   0.15s ease;
--transition-slow:   0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
```

#### Animation Keyframes (defined in `index.css`)
| Name | Effect | Duration | Usage |
|---|---|---|---|
| `fadeIn` | opacity 0→1 | 0.4s | Modal, dropdown |
| `fadeInUp` | opacity 0→1, translateY 20px→0 | 0.5s | Page content entrance |
| `slideInLeft` | opacity 0→1, translateX -20px→0 | 0.4s | Sidebar, panels |
| `skeleton-loading` | shimmer across element | 1.5s loop | Loading skeletons |

#### Interaction Patterns
- **Card hover**: `transform: translateY(-2px)` + enhanced shadow, 0.3s
- **Button hover**: `translateY(-1px)` + shadow enhancement, 0.2s
- **Button press**: `translateY(1px)`, 0.1s
- **Focus ring**: `focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/20 focus:border-primary`
- **Page transitions**: `animate-fade-in-up` on `<main>` element
- **Dropdown**: fade in với `AnimatePresence` from framer-motion

### 2.7 Breakpoints

| Name | Min-width | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| `sm` | 640px | Large phone |
| `md` | 768px | Tablet |
| `lg` | 1024px | Desktop |
| `xl` | 1280px | Large desktop |

### 2.8 Z-Index Scale

| Layer | Value | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| Base | 0 | Default stacking |
| Header | 50 | `sticky` header |
| Dropdown | 50 | Profile dropdown |
| Sticky | 50 | Layout header |
| Modal Backdrop | 60 | Modal overlay |
| Modal | 70 | Modal content |
| Toast | 80 | react-hot-toast |
| Tooltip | 90 | Tooltip overlay |

---

## 3. Component System

### 3.1 Layout Structure

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  HEADER (sticky, h-16, backdrop-blur-md)                │
│  [Logo] [Nav Pills]              [Notif 🔔] [Avatar▾]   │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  MAIN (className="animate-fade-in-up")                  │
│  (py-6 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto)          │
│                                                         │
│  Page Header (title + breadcrumb + actions)            │
│  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────  │
│  Content Grid / Cards / Form                           │
│                                                         │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

#### Header
- **Height**: 64px (`h-16`)
- **Background**: `bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-border sticky top-0 z-50`
- **Left**: Logo (clickable, navigate to dashboard)
- **Center**: Nav pills — `rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-surface to-surface-hover border border-border shadow-soft`
- **Right**: Notification bell (unread badge) + Profile dropdown

#### Navigation Pills (Desktop)
- Container: `rounded-full px-1 py-1 flex items-center gap-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-surface border border-border shadow-soft`
- Item inactive: `px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-text-secondary transition-all hover:text-primary hover:bg-primary/5`
- Item active: `px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold text-primary bg-white shadow-sm`
- Item icon: `w-4 h-4`

#### Mobile Navigation
- Hamburger: `w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg hover:bg-surface`
- Menu: `absolute top-16 right-0 w-64 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-md border border-border shadow-lg rounded-b-2xl z-50`
- Active item: `bg-primary/10 text-primary font-medium`

#### Background Layers
```tsx
// Login page
className="min-h-screen bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat"
style={{ backgroundImage: `url(${backgroundImage})` }}

// Authenticated pages — custom backgrounds per page
className="min-h-screen bg-dashboard" // or bg-custom-background
```

### 3.2 Page Header Pattern

```tsx
<div className="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between gap-4 mb-6">
  <div>
    <h1 className="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary tracking-tight">
      {pageTitle}
    </h1>
    {subtitle && (
      <p className="text-sm text-text-secondary mt-1">{subtitle}</p>
    )}
  </div>
  <div className="flex items-center gap-3">
    {/* Action buttons */}
  </div>
</div>
```

### 3.3 Cards

#### `.card` — Standard Card
```css
.card {
  background: #FFFFFF;
  border-radius: 16px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px -6px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
}
```

**Card Section Header Pattern** (used inside cards):
```tsx
<div className="px-5 py-4 bg-primary/5 border-b border-border">
  <h3 className="text-sm font-semibold text-text-primary">{sectionTitle}</h3>
</div>
```

#### `.card-hover` — Interactive Card
```tsx
<motion.div
  whileHover={{ y: -2, boxShadow: '0 8px 24px -8px rgba(0,0,0,0.12)' }}
  transition={{ duration: 0.3 }}
  className="card p-5 cursor-pointer"
>
```

#### `.qa-card` — Quick Action Card (Dashboard)
```tsx
<div className="bg-white rounded-[30px] p-5 shadow-sm border border-border
                flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 min-h-[140px]
                hover:shadow-md transition-shadow cursor-pointer">
  <div className="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center">
    {icon}
  </div>
  <span className="text-sm font-semibold text-text-primary text-center">{label}</span>
</div>
```

#### `.stat-card` — Statistic Card
```tsx
<div className="card p-5 flex items-center gap-4">
  <div className="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center">
    {icon}
  </div>
  <div>
    <p className="text-xs text-text-secondary font-medium uppercase tracking-wide">{label}</p>
    <p className="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary">{value}</p>
  </div>
</div>
```

#### Class Card (ClassDetail / ClassList)
```tsx
<div className="card p-4 flex gap-4 items-start">
  <div className="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
    {icon}
  </div>
  <div className="flex-1 min-w-0">
    <h3 className="font-semibold text-text-primary">{name}</h3>
    <p className="text-sm text-text-secondary">{teacher}</p>
    <div className="flex gap-4 mt-2">
      <span className="text-xs text-text-muted">{studentCount} học sinh</span>
      {examCount > 0 && <span className="text-xs text-text-muted">{examCount} bài kiểm tra</span>}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
```

#### Exam Card
```tsx
<div className="card p-5">
  <div className="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
    <div>
      <h3 className="font-semibold text-text-primary">{title}</h3>
      <p className="text-sm text-text-secondary">{className} • {duration} phút</p>
    </div>
    <Badge variant={statusVariant}>{statusLabel}</Badge>
  </div>
  {/* Progress or action */}
  <div className="flex items-center justify-between">
    <div className="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-text-muted">
      <Calendar className="w-3 h-3" />
      <span>{dueDate}</span>
    </div>
    <Button variant="primary" size="sm">{actionLabel}</Button>
  </div>
</div>
```

### 3.4 Buttons

#### Primary Button (`.btn-primary`)
```css
.btn-primary {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7BA389 0%, #5C8A6E 100%);
  color: white;
  border-radius: 12px;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 14px;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(123, 163, 137, 0.25);
}
.btn-primary:hover {
  transform: translateY(-1px);
  box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(123, 163, 137, 0.35);
  filter: brightness(1.05);
}
.btn-primary:active {
  transform: translateY(1px);
  box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(123, 163, 137, 0.2);
}
.btn-primary:disabled {
  opacity: 0.5;
  cursor: not-allowed;
  transform: none;
}
```

**⚠️ Login page inconsistency**: Login page hardcodes darker greens directly in className strings:
- `bg-[#6B9080]` gradient start
- `bg-[#5F8D78]` gradient mid
- `hover:bg-[#4A6F5E]` hover
- These should be replaced with `.btn-primary` class or Tailwind primary token

#### Outline Button (`.btn-outline`)
```css
.btn-outline {
  background: transparent;
  color: #7BA389;
  border: 2px solid #7BA389;
  border-radius: 12px;
  font-weight: 600;
  padding: 8px 20px;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}
.btn-outline:hover {
  background: #7BA389;
  color: white;
}
```

#### Secondary Button
```tsx
<button className="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-text-secondary
                   bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg
                   hover:bg-surface-hover hover:text-text-primary
                   transition-all">
  Label
</button>
```

#### Ghost Button
```tsx
<button className="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-text-secondary
                   rounded-lg hover:bg-surface transition-colors">
  Label
</button>
```

#### Danger Button
```tsx
<button className="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-[#C53030]
                   bg-[#FDE8E8] rounded-lg
                   hover:bg-[#C53030] hover:text-white
                   transition-all">
  Label
</button>
```

#### Icon Button
```tsx
<button className="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center
                   text-text-secondary hover:bg-surface
                   hover:text-primary transition-colors">
  {icon}
</button>
```

#### Button Sizes
| Size | Class | Padding | Font | Usage |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| sm | `.btn-sm` | 6px 12px | 12px | Table row actions, badges |
| md | (default) | 10px 20px | 14px | Standard actions |
| lg | `.btn-lg` | 12px 24px | 16px | Hero CTA, login |
| icon | `.btn-icon` | 8px | — | Single icon |

### 3.5 Form Inputs

#### Text Input
```tsx
<input
  className="w-full bg-white/60 border border-border rounded-lg px-4 py-2.5
             text-sm text-text-primary placeholder:text-text-muted
             focus:bg-white/80 focus:border-primary focus:ring-2
             focus:ring-primary/20 focus:outline-none transition-all"
/>
```

#### Input with Icon
```tsx
<div className="relative">
  <div className="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3.5 flex items-center pointer-events-none">
    <Search className="w-4 h-4 text-text-muted" />
  </div>
  <input className="input-field pl-10 w-full" placeholder="Tìm kiếm..." />
</div>
```

#### Password Input
```tsx
<div className="relative">
  <input
    type={showPassword ? 'text' : 'password'}
    className="input-field pr-10 w-full"
  />
  <button
    type="button"
    className="absolute inset-y-0 right-0 pr-3.5 flex items-center"
    onClick={() => setShowPassword(!showPassword)}
  >
    {showPassword ? <EyeOff className="w-4 h-4 text-text-muted" /> : <Eye className="w-4 h-4 text-text-muted" />}
  </button>
</div>
```

#### Select
```tsx
<select className="input-field appearance-none bg-no-repeat
                   bg-[right_12px_center] bg-[length:16px]
                   pr-10">
  {/* Options */}
</select>
```

#### Textarea
```tsx
<textarea
  className="input-field w-full min-h-[100px] resize-y"
  placeholder="Nhập nội dung..."
/>
```

#### Form Layout
```tsx
<div className="space-y-5">
  <div>
    <label className="block text-sm font-medium text-text-primary mb-1.5">
      Label <span className="text-[#C53030]">*</span>
    </label>
    <input className="input-field w-full" />
    <p className="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">Helper text</p>
  </div>
  {/* Error state */}
  <div>
    <label className="block text-sm font-medium text-text-primary mb-1.5">
      Label
    </label>
    <input className="input-field w-full border-[#C53030] focus:ring-[#C53030]/20" />
    <p className="text-xs text-[#C53030] mt-1">Error message</p>
  </div>
</div>
```

### 3.6 Badges / Status Indicators

```tsx
// CSS badge classes
<span className="inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">
  {icon && <span className="w-3 h-3">{icon}</span>}
  {label}
</span>
```

| Variant | Classes | Color | Usage |
|---|---|---|---|
| success | `bg-[#D4E8D7] text-[#3D7A4F]` | Green | Hoàn thành, đạt, đã nộp |
| warning | `bg-[#FFE8D6] text-[#B86E00]` | Amber | Pending, chưa nộp, sắp hết hạn |
| error | `bg-[#FDE8E8] text-[#C53030]` | Red | Không đạt, quá hạn, lỗi |
| info | `bg-[#DCE4F2] text-[#4A6FA5]` | Blue | Đang xử lý, thông tin |
| live | `bg-[#DCFCE7] text-[#16A34A]` | Bright green | Exam đang diễn ra |

### 3.7 Progress Bars

```tsx
// Default progress bar
<div className="w-full h-2 bg-[#F0F4F8] rounded-full overflow-hidden">
  <div
    className="h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary-light rounded-full transition-all duration-500"
    style={{ width: `${percentage}%` }}
  />
</div>

// With label
<div className="space-y-2">
  <div className="flex justify-between text-sm">
    <span className="text-text-secondary">{label}</span>
    <span className="font-semibold text-text-primary">{percentage}%</span>
  </div>
  <div className="w-full h-2 bg-border rounded-full overflow-hidden">
    <div className="h-full rounded-full transition-all duration-500" style={{ width: `${percentage}%`, background: 'var(--progress-color)' }} />
  </div>
</div>

// Circular progress
<div className="relative w-16 h-16">
  <svg className="w-16 h-16 -rotate-90">
    <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="28" fill="none" stroke="#F0F4F8" strokeWidth="4" />
    <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="28" fill="none" stroke="#7BA389" strokeWidth="4"
      strokeDasharray={`${(percentage / 100) * 175.9} 175.9`} strokeLinecap="round" />
  </svg>
  <span className="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold text-text-primary">
    {percentage}%
  </span>
</div>
```

### 3.8 Tables

```tsx
<div className="card overflow-hidden">
  <div className="overflow-x-auto">
    <table className="w-full">
      <thead>
        <tr className="bg-surface border-b border-border">
          <th className="text-left text-xs font-semibold text-text-secondary uppercase tracking-wide px-4 py-3">
            Column
          </th>
        </tr>
